      "lines": [
        { "text": "ಬದುಕಿನ ಬಣ್ಣವೇ ಬದಲಾದರೆ ಅದು ಪ್ರೇಮವೇ..", "fontFamily": "AnekKannada-Light", "fontSize": 30, "color": "#FFFFFF", "isBold": false },
        { "text": "- ಜಯಂತ್ ಕಾಯ್ಕಿಣಿ", "fontFamily": "AnekKannada-Bold", "fontSize": 24, "color": "#FF69B4", "isBold": true }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "love_rajarathnam_01",
      "name": "Rajarathnam Two Shores",
      "category": "Love",
      "lines": [
        { "text": "ನಾವು ಇಬ್ಬರು ಅಲ್ಲ, ನಾವು ಒಂದೇ ಶ್ವಾಸ, ಒಂದೇ ಜೀವ,", "fontFamily": "AnekKannada-Regular", "fontSize": 26, "color": "#FFFFFF", "isBold": false },
        { "text": "ಒಂದೇ ನದಿಯ ಎರಡು ತೀರ.", "fontFamily": "Gubbi", "fontSize": 28, "color": "#FFD700", "isBold": true },
        { "text": "- ಜಿ.ಪಿ. ರಾಜರತ್ನಂ", "fontFamily": "AnekKannada-Bold", "fontSize": 24, "color": "#F0EAD6", "isBold": false }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "love_nissar_01",
      "name": "Nissar Barren Heart",
      "category": "Love",
      "lines": [
        { "text": "ಪ್ರೇಮವಿಲ್ಲದ ಹೃದಯ ಬಂಜರು ಭೂಮಿ — ಕವನ ಅರಳದು.", "fontFamily": "AnekKannada-Medium", "fontSize": 28, "color": "#FFFFFF", "isBold": false },
        { "text": "- ಕೆ.ಎಸ್. ನಿಸ್ಸಾರ್ ಅಹಮದ್", "fontFamily": "AnekKannada-Bold", "fontSize": 24, "color": "#FFD700", "isBold": false }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "love_karanth_01",
      "name": "Karanth Sacrifice",
      "category": "Love",
      "lines": [
        { "text": "ಪ್ರೇಮದ ನಿಜವಾದ ರೂಪ ತ್ಯಾಗದಲ್ಲಿ ಅರಳುತ್ತದೆ.", "fontFamily": "AnekKannada-Regular", "fontSize": 28, "color": "#FFFFFF", "isBold": false },
        { "text": "- ಶಿವರಾಮ ಕಾರಂತ್", "fontFamily": "Kar-Shivarama-Karantha", "fontSize": 30, "color": "#FF69B4", "isBold": false }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "love_kalyan_01",
      "name": "Kalyan Joy",
      "category": "Love",
      "lines": [
        { "text": "ಒಲವೇ ನಿನ್ನ ನಲಿವೊಂದೆ ವರವೆನ್ನುತಾ ನಾ ನಲಿವೆ.", "fontFamily": "Malige", "fontSize": 32, "color": "#FFB6C1", "isBold": false },
        { "text": "- ಕೆ. ಕಲ್ಯಾಣ್", "fontFamily": "AnekKannada-Bold", "fontSize": 24, "color": "#FFFFFF", "isBold": false }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "love_bendre_01",
      "name": "Bendre Poor Love",
      "category": "Love",
      "lines": [
        { "text": "ನಾನು ಬಡವಿ, ಆತ ಬಡವ , ಒಲವೇ ನಮ್ಮ ಬದುಕು.", "fontFamily": "AnekKannada-Medium", "fontSize": 26, "color": "#FFFFFF", "isBold": false },
        { "text": "ಬಳಸಿಕೊಂಡೆವೆದನೆ ನಾವು ಅದಕು ಇದಕು ಎದಕು .", "fontFamily": "AnekKannada-Regular", "fontSize": 26, "color": "#F0EAD6", "isBold": false },
        { "text": "- ಬೇಂದ್ರೆ", "fontFamily": "Kar-Da-Raa-Bendre", "fontSize": 32, "color": "#FFD700", "isBold": false }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "love_sudhamurty_01",
      "name": "Sudhamurty Freedom",
      "category": "Love",
      "lines": [
        { "text": "ಪ್ರೇಮ ಎಂದರೆ ಸ್ವಾತಂತ್ರ್ಯದ ಮತ್ತೊಂದು ಹೆಸರು.", "fontFamily": "AnekKannada-Medium", "fontSize": 28, "color": "#FFFFFF", "isBold": false },
        { "text": "- ಸುಧಾಮೂರ್ತಿ", "fontFamily": "AnekKannada-Bold", "fontSize": 24, "color": "#FFD700", "isBold": false }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "love_kuvempu_02",
      "name": "Kuvempu Love God",
      "category": "Love",
      "lines": [
        { "text": "ಪ್ರೇಮವೇ ದೇವತೆ —", "fontFamily": "AnekKannada-Bold", "fontSize": 30, "color": "#FF69B4", "isBold": true },
        { "text": "ಅದು ಮನುಷ್ಯನನ್ನು ದೇವನಾಗಿಸುತ್ತದೆ.", "fontFamily": "AnekKannada-Regular", "fontSize": 28, "color": "#FFFFFF", "isBold": false },
        { "text": "- ಕುವೆಂಪು", "fontFamily": "Kar-Kuvempu", "fontSize": 28, "color": "#FFD700", "isBold": false }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
